{"title":"肖申克的救赎","uid":"d54b151e7dab10c813cd2b0e231c28e5","slug":"肖申克的救赎","date":"2021-08-01T19:51:43.329Z","updated":"2021-08-10T16:00:18.611Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/肖申克的救赎.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/05/30/4kbizhi/11.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"肖申克的救赎以9-7分排名豆瓣TOP250第一\"><a href=\"#肖申克的救赎以9-7分排名豆瓣TOP250第一\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"肖申克的救赎以9.7分排名豆瓣TOP250第一\"></a><center>肖申克的救赎以9.7分排名豆瓣TOP250第一</h2><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/2.png\"></p>\n<p>我给了一星<br>一星人数千分之一，难道是我错了吗？<br>肖申克真的是单纯善良，让人一看到那无辜的小眼神就心生怜悯的小可怜吗？？</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/1.png\"></p>\n<p>我说肖申克是凶手的原因<br>1.找不到枪支不合理：<br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/3.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/4.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/5.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/13.png\"></p>\n<p>2.左轮手枪只能装6发子弹，两人总共中了8枪，有装弹补枪行为，电影后面出现的只是抢劫的“真凶”为何如此<code>凶残</code>,如此凶残的劫匪还能抢个几百次安然无恙？？？？</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/6.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/22.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/23.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/7.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/14.png\"></p>\n<p>3.肖申克自己说监狱里的人，人人都是无辜这句话简直就是颠倒黑白，巧舌如簧，充分说明美国银行家多么阴险狡诈<br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/8.png\"></p>\n<p>4.两个人偷情，劫匪去抢劫，情夫跟劫匪叫板被杀，偷情本是偷偷摸摸的竟然还要叫板，脑子进水啦？情夫跟劫匪叫板但事实却是：他的妻子搂着情夫死去，肖申克在现场弄的到处是指纹。<br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/11.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/25.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/27.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/28.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/26.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/20.png\"><br>5.就算你没杀人，你帮监狱长逃税漏税和洗钱，肖申克是否有罪，越狱的正义在哪？这涉及一个法律伦理问题：歹徒逼着你杀人，不然就杀了你，那么你杀人是否有罪？<br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/50.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/51.png\"></p>\n<p>6.进监狱1个月不说话，一说话就找到老黑搞锤子准备越狱（不申冤，只想越狱，这是无辜冤枉之人的正常做法？？？）<br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/15.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/16.png\"></p>\n<p>7.电影借的是安迪之口说明真凶另有他人太奇怪，为什么偏偏是不识字并想拿高中文凭的安迪，<br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/17.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/18.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/43.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/44.png\"></p>\n<p>8.电影借老黑之口讲述太奇怪，两个人越狱成功，却让老黑向世人讲述救赎的故事，看来主人公又给老黑洗了一次脑啊！！！（你们就听老黑使劲的吹吧）<br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/35.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/36.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/32.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/33.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/34.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/41.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/42.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/37.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/30.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/08/02/xiaoshenkedejiushu/31.png\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">总之，我认为这部电影登封榜首很奇怪非常魔幻。可能电影十分优秀，但长时间牢牢的问鼎榜首，盛名之下，其实难副！\n这部电影必须要非常明确的告诉观众肖申克是冤枉的，是无辜的。但遗憾的是，看了两遍，电影不仅留下了上面种种疑点、并没有直接或间接&#96;可靠的&#96;证据证明他的无辜，反而在最后肖申克又实锤了洗钱罪和越狱罪。\n美国银行家说的一个标点符号都不能相信。<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>我的观点：</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>肖申克年纪轻轻就成为一个银行家,聪明狡诈，发现妻子出轨后，在喝醉酒的情况下愤怒的杀害了妻子和情人，后销毁关键证据手枪，不想依然被判刑。到狱中观察一个月后找到了<code>老黑</code>买了一把锤子就开始准备越狱并为此坚持了二十年，在监狱里曲通逢迎利用<code>专长</code>帮助狱友填报税单逃税，帮助邪恶的典狱长洗钱，帮助不识字的安迪通过高考，借以换取安迪之口说出一个不存在的“真凶”，，在洗白计划失败后，害怕余生像图书馆管理员落得最终上吊的下场，携黑钱<code>成功</code>越狱，并洗白身份，最终，洗脑老黑借他之口塑造了一个这么无辜形象（因为关键证物要么找不到，要么死了）。</p></blockquote>\n<p>以以上的观点看整部电影才通顺</p>\n<p>综上给一星。</p>\n","text":"肖申克的救赎以9.7分排名豆瓣TOP250第一 我给了一星一星人数千分之一，难道是我错了吗？肖申克真的是单纯善良，让人一看到那无辜的小眼神就心生怜悯的小可怜吗？？ 我说肖申克是凶手的原因1.找不到枪支不合理： 2.左轮手枪只能装6发子弹，两人总共中了8枪，有装弹补枪行为，电影后面...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"其他","slug":"其他","count":16,"path":"api/categories/其他.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"肖申克的救赎","slug":"肖申克的救赎","count":1,"path":"api/tags/肖申克的救赎.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%82%96%E7%94%B3%E5%85%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%95%91%E8%B5%8E%E4%BB%A59-7%E5%88%86%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D%E8%B1%86%E7%93%A3TOP250%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80\"><span class=\"toc-text\">肖申克的救赎以9.7分排名豆瓣TOP250第一</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"花开","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/medias/av